<div class="font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-indigo-300"> Available on all plans </div>
<p>Cache stores copies of frequently accessed content (such as images, videos, or webpages) in geographically distributed data centers that are located closer to end users than origin servers, reducing server load and improving website performance.</p>
<div> <stream-player data-id="90d8a506e1e3935cff71223f9d785aa6" data-title="How Cloudflare protects and accelerates your website or app"> <div style="position: relative; padding-top: 56.25%"> <iframe src="https://customer-1mwganm1ma0xgnmj.cloudflarestream.com/90d8a506e1e3935cff71223f9d785aa6/iframe?preload=true&amp;letterboxColor=transparent&amp;poster=https%3A%2F%2Fimagedelivery.net%2FxDOJvHcv1KwTQn6S-BGFIw%2Ff104ce23-cc3d-4f1a-fa3b-c6a894107d00%2Fpublic" style="border: none; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; height: 100%; width: 100%;" allow="accelerometer; gyroscope; autoplay; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture;" allowfullscreen="true" title="How Cloudflare protects and accelerates your website or app" id="90d8a506e1e3935cff71223f9d785aa6"></iframe> </div>   </stream-player> </div> <script src="https://embed.cloudflarestream.com/embed/sdk.latest.js"></script> <script type="module" src="/_astro/Stream.astro_astro_type_script_index_0_lang.CH501ydf.js"></script>
<div tabindex="-1" class="heading-wrapper level-h2"><h2 id="features">Features</h2><a class="anchor-link" href="#features"><span aria-hidden="true" class="anchor-icon"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="currentcolor" d="m12.11 15.39-3.88 3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1-3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0-3.5l3.88-3.88a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-3.88 3.89a4.48 4.48 0 0 0 6.33 6.33l3.89-3.88a1 1 0 1 0-1.42-1.42Zm8.58-12.08a4.49 4.49 0 0 0-6.33 0l-3.89 3.88a1 1 0 0 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0 3.5l-3.88 3.88a1 1 0 1 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.89a4.49 4.49 0 0 0 0-6.33ZM8.83 15.17a1 1 0 0 0 1.1.22 1 1 0 0 0 .32-.22l4.92-4.92a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-4.92 4.92a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.42Z"></path></svg></span></a></div>
<div class="feature mb-7 border-t border-t-[var(--color-cl1-gray-8)] pt-6 astro-ezsi7upz"> <h3 class="m-0 mb-2 text-[1.3125rem] leading-[1.3] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] astro-ezsi7upz"> Default cache behavior </h3> <div class="feature-description mb-3 text-base leading-[1.65] text-[var(--sl-color-text)] astro-ezsi7upz"> <p>Learn about default cache behavior, default cached file extensions and cache responses.</p> </div> <a href="/cache/concepts/default-cache-behavior/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b-2 border-b-[var(--color-cl1-brand-orange)] pb-px text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--sl-color-white)] no-underline transition-[border-color] duration-200 ease-in-out hover:border-b-[var(--sl-color-white)] astro-ezsi7upz"> Use Default cache behavior <svg aria-hidden="true" class="astro-ezsi7upz astro-jsgs62qu" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="--sl-icon-size: 0.875rem;"><path d="M17.92 11.62a1.001 1.001 0 0 0-.21-.33l-5-5a1.003 1.003 0 1 0-1.42 1.42l3.3 3.29H7a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h7.59l-3.3 3.29a1.002 1.002 0 0 0 .325 1.639 1 1 0 0 0 1.095-.219l5-5a1 1 0 0 0 .21-.33 1 1 0 0 0 0-.76Z"/></svg> </a> </div>
<div class="feature mb-7 border-t border-t-[var(--color-cl1-gray-8)] pt-6 astro-ezsi7upz"> <h3 class="m-0 mb-2 text-[1.3125rem] leading-[1.3] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] astro-ezsi7upz"> Cache Rules </h3> <div class="feature-description mb-3 text-base leading-[1.65] text-[var(--sl-color-text)] astro-ezsi7upz"> <p>Configure Cache Rules to optimize your website by specifying which resources should be cached and for how long.</p> </div> <a href="/cache/how-to/cache-rules/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b-2 border-b-[var(--color-cl1-brand-orange)] pb-px text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--sl-color-white)] no-underline transition-[border-color] duration-200 ease-in-out hover:border-b-[var(--sl-color-white)] astro-ezsi7upz"> Use Cache Rules <svg aria-hidden="true" class="astro-ezsi7upz astro-jsgs62qu" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="--sl-icon-size: 0.875rem;"><path d="M17.92 11.62a1.001 1.001 0 0 0-.21-.33l-5-5a1.003 1.003 0 1 0-1.42 1.42l3.3 3.29H7a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h7.59l-3.3 3.29a1.002 1.002 0 0 0 .325 1.639 1 1 0 0 0 1.095-.219l5-5a1 1 0 0 0 .21-.33 1 1 0 0 0 0-.76Z"/></svg> </a> </div>
<div class="feature mb-7 border-t border-t-[var(--color-cl1-gray-8)] pt-6 astro-ezsi7upz"> <h3 class="m-0 mb-2 text-[1.3125rem] leading-[1.3] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] astro-ezsi7upz"> Tiered Cache </h3> <div class="feature-description mb-3 text-base leading-[1.65] text-[var(--sl-color-text)] astro-ezsi7upz"> <p>Enable Tiered Cache to optimize content delivery by caching frequently accessed content in multiple locations for faster delivery and reduced origin traffic.</p> </div> <a href="/cache/how-to/tiered-cache/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b-2 border-b-[var(--color-cl1-brand-orange)] pb-px text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--sl-color-white)] no-underline transition-[border-color] duration-200 ease-in-out hover:border-b-[var(--sl-color-white)] astro-ezsi7upz"> Use Tiered Cache <svg aria-hidden="true" class="astro-ezsi7upz astro-jsgs62qu" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="--sl-icon-size: 0.875rem;"><path d="M17.92 11.62a1.001 1.001 0 0 0-.21-.33l-5-5a1.003 1.003 0 1 0-1.42 1.42l3.3 3.29H7a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h7.59l-3.3 3.29a1.002 1.002 0 0 0 .325 1.639 1 1 0 0 0 1.095-.219l5-5a1 1 0 0 0 .21-.33 1 1 0 0 0 0-.76Z"/></svg> </a> </div>
<div class="feature mb-7 border-t border-t-[var(--color-cl1-gray-8)] pt-6 astro-ezsi7upz"> <h3 class="m-0 mb-2 text-[1.3125rem] leading-[1.3] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] astro-ezsi7upz"> Cache Reserve </h3> <div class="feature-description mb-3 text-base leading-[1.65] text-[var(--sl-color-text)] astro-ezsi7upz"> <p>Use Cloudflare's persistent storage to increase cache times.</p> </div> <a href="/cache/advanced-configuration/cache-reserve/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b-2 border-b-[var(--color-cl1-brand-orange)] pb-px text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--sl-color-white)] no-underline transition-[border-color] duration-200 ease-in-out hover:border-b-[var(--sl-color-white)] astro-ezsi7upz"> Use Cache Reserve <svg aria-hidden="true" class="astro-ezsi7upz astro-jsgs62qu" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="--sl-icon-size: 0.875rem;"><path d="M17.92 11.62a1.001 1.001 0 0 0-.21-.33l-5-5a1.003 1.003 0 1 0-1.42 1.42l3.3 3.29H7a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h7.59l-3.3 3.29a1.002 1.002 0 0 0 .325 1.639 1 1 0 0 0 1.095-.219l5-5a1 1 0 0 0 .21-.33 1 1 0 0 0 0-.76Z"/></svg> </a> </div>
<div class="feature mb-7 border-t border-t-[var(--color-cl1-gray-8)] pt-6 astro-ezsi7upz"> <h3 class="m-0 mb-2 text-[1.3125rem] leading-[1.3] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] astro-ezsi7upz"> Purge </h3> <div class="feature-description mb-3 text-base leading-[1.65] text-[var(--sl-color-text)] astro-ezsi7upz"> <p>Instantly purge cached files to force Cloudflare to fetch fresh versions from your web server files. You can purge specific files or all at once.</p> </div> <a href="/cache/how-to/purge-cache/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b-2 border-b-[var(--color-cl1-brand-orange)] pb-px text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--sl-color-white)] no-underline transition-[border-color] duration-200 ease-in-out hover:border-b-[var(--sl-color-white)] astro-ezsi7upz"> Use Purge <svg aria-hidden="true" class="astro-ezsi7upz astro-jsgs62qu" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="--sl-icon-size: 0.875rem;"><path d="M17.92 11.62a1.001 1.001 0 0 0-.21-.33l-5-5a1.003 1.003 0 1 0-1.42 1.42l3.3 3.29H7a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h7.59l-3.3 3.29a1.002 1.002 0 0 0 .325 1.639 1 1 0 0 0 1.095-.219l5-5a1 1 0 0 0 .21-.33 1 1 0 0 0 0-.76Z"/></svg> </a> </div>
